g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多鳩餘"},{"pid":"5ae9c4390355b9405bbb6841dff85f4ba8dfcc3a","tid":264897,"uid":52942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:13:23.000Z","msg":"香港d細路仔邊得閒4點起身呀，做功課都做到點幾兩點啦，關注下個仆街理胃鯨好過啦，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed30741c1d8dfc5b495dcb60ec09d609848d4ec3","tid":264897,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ghz6j0la\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fghz6j0la&h=9df2c854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n終於有用武之地 養兵千日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到底世上仲有無一樣野可以戇鳩得過呢張所謂契約<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前有個學生妹簽完份野。一樣跳樓"},{"pid":"ea3959a0c775b75e6722d38e747b7378db8f1331","tid":264897,"uid":38271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496215204_5f75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496215204_5f75.jpg&h=78c7e529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n議員關注鼓吹自殘的俄羅斯網絡遊戲「藍鯨」（Blue whale）近日傳入香港，教育局副局長楊潤雄承認，教育局未有掌握有關資料，但防止罪行法例亦適用於網上世界，任何人教唆或促使他人自殺，可能觸犯傷害人身條例，一經定罪可被判監14年。 <br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又表示，會提醒學校老師及家長留意學生會否受不良網絡遊戲影響，但最有效防止青少年自殺的方法是向學生灌輸正確價值觀及正面人生觀，及網絡安全意識。教育局亦正研究利用社交媒體防止自殺，聯同facebook及youtube等發展一些防止自殺工具，識別高危青少年，提早提供援手。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯柯創盛</span>批評「藍鯨」是催命符，英國、阿根廷等地都就「藍鯨」發出警告，內地亦對「藍鯨」封殺，香港卻未有任何防範措施。香港眾志羅冠聰就指今年至今已有17宗學童自殺，教育局去年發表的防止自殺報告治標不治本，應檢討出問題的教育制度。</blockquote><br />\n假學歷都做到立會就真係教學童自殺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834e498a81e9de38080f1927a04ff04d28faa396","tid":264897,"uid":90045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係本身想自殺先玩啊嘛？<br />\n點會係玩玩下唔小心自殺"},{"pid":"ce764c11ebf47283e6610547248d11ae88085134","tid":264897,"uid":43382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"研發網上防自殺工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n整個大白鯊計劃同藍鯨差唔多既形式<br />\n啲活動改成 一開始啲活動就打下機，之後慢慢變成背生字每日一篇、做下運動、義工個啲 <br />\n<br />\n最後個任務就係 on9仔咁得閒就充實下生活啦 唔想再做on9仔就叫多啲朋友仔黎玩 因為你同你身邊既人都係on9咁你就係正常人啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8065fde42109f4dc4a0248f452fd578a84f8d4ad","tid":264897,"uid":13845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:31:57.000Z","msg":"果堆功課補習默書 家長咪叫藍鯨囉"},{"pid":"1af6fab28e96193e6b7c8de06f532c9dc31c6f7a","tid":264897,"uid":53207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"唔係啲新聞成日講根本冇人識呢隻game<br />\n曲線宣傳<br />\n<br />\n講真啲廢青邊會玩呀<br />\n要4點幾起身已經唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走落路軌又俾人圍屌阻住返工"},{"pid":"1feba497395d5bdf38afff278e53cb427ac2230d","tid":264897,"uid":118023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:37:57.000Z","msg":"香港教育制度本身已經係藍鯨遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7ea727914ab66b5132b9885488fb72f62de364","tid":264897,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯有藍鯨 香港有TSA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02964eee81e7e5f534777ea2d142fd749ca4d77d","tid":264897,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2